                <iframe id="map" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1642.772489548168!2d-18.123140657310962!3d65.68574018414412!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x48d28faa7eca0bd3%3A0xfc9e0104592e1efe!2sH%C3%A1sk%C3%B3linn+%C3%A1+Akureyri+-+University+of+Akureyri!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1525294175799" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
